    <h1>Hashtag Strategy</h1>
    <p class="description">A <strong>planned system for researching, selecting, and rotating hashtags</strong> on social media posts to maximise reach and discoverability. Instagram posts with 20 targeted hashtags achieve the highest average reach — but the right hashtags matter far more than the number.</p>
    <div class="post-meta">
